🛒 E-Commerce Website

A simple, responsive e-commerce website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can browse products, add them to the cart, and view a dynamic cart summary — all in the browser using client-side storage.

🚀 Features

🛍 Product listing with images and prices
🛒 Add to cart and remove from cart
🧾 Cart total calculation
💾 Cart data stored using JavaScript (in-memory or localStorage)
📱 Fully responsive layout


🛠 Tech Stack
HTML – Structure and content
CSS – Styling and responsive design
JavaScript – Dynamic interactions and cart functionality
